  "texts": [
    "The concentrations of compound in the plasma were analysed using a liquid chromatography-mass spectrometry method with a calibration range of 5-10,000 ng ml -1.",
    "The pharmacokinetic parameters were derived from the individual concentration data and were estimated by non-compartmental analysis.",
    "Four male Wistar rats per group were administered 0 (vehicle control), 0.6 or 6.0 mg per kg per day of RO7075573 or zosurabalpin as a slow intravenous infusion for five days (0, 0.12 or 1.2 mg ml -1 in 0.9% aqueous sodium chloride solution).",
    "Assessment of tolerability was based on mortality, in-life observations, body weight, food consumption and clinical pathology during the in-life phase.",
    "Moreover, gross pathology and histopathology were performed at unscheduled or scheduled euthanasia on day 6."
